WEBVTT

00:01.698 --> 00:03.698
Are you still worried
about the risk?

00:03.949 --> 00:06.509
Because I've written to my aunt
in Sydney, and she'll help us.

00:06.519 --> 00:08.629
Marry me.
I will.

00:08.639 --> 00:10.739
I will marry you.

00:10.749 --> 00:13.664
This isn't about the church.
I'm your child.

00:13.674 --> 00:16.589
Take your Jew name and go.
I have no daughter.

00:16.599 --> 00:18.459
Go!

00:18.469 --> 00:22.389
I never want to be reminded
of that hypocritical day

00:22.399 --> 00:24.499
I married the man
who loves my brother.

00:24.509 --> 00:28.869
And I will respect the need
to keep this between we three.

00:28.879 --> 00:32.189
But I will never respect you again.

00:34.000 --> 00:40.074
